es Risques & Catastrophes (2025–26)<\\/span><\\/div>\",\"<div style='font-family:sans-serif;padding:6px;min-width:210px;'><b style='color:#00b4d8;font-size:0.95em;'>Diagnostic CECA-DR – Plateau Central<\\/b><br><span style='color:#555;font-size:0.8em;'>GIRE<\\/span><br><br><span style='color:#333;font-size:0.85em;'>Diagnostic participatif GIRE – 6 villages<\\/span><\\/div>\"],null,[\"Bassin versant du Nakanbé\",\"Agence de l'Eau du Nakanbé – Ziniaré\",\"Ministère de l'Eau – Ouagadougou\",\"Commune de Bama (télédétection)\",\"Formation UDDM – Maradi\",\"CRA Agrhymet – Niamey\",\"Master GRC – Liège\",\"Diagnostic CECA-DR – Plateau Central\"],{\"interactive\":false,\"permanent\":false,\"direction\":\"auto\",\"opacity\":1,\"offset\":[0,0],\"textsize\":\"10px\",\"textOnly\":false,\"style\":{\"font-family\":\"sans-serif\",\"background-color\":\"#1a1a2e\",\"color\":\"#cdd6f4\",\"border-color\":\"#00b4d8\",\"border-radius\":\"4px\",\"padding\":\"4px 8px\"},\"className\":\"\",\"sticky\":true},null]},{\"method\":\"addLegend\",\"args\":[{\"colors\":[\"#00B4D8\",\"#E63946\",\"#F4A261\",\"#06D6A0\",\"#C4B5FD\"],\"labels\":[\"Formation\",\"GIRE\",\"Hydrologie\",\"Institution\",\"SIG\"],\"na_color\":null,\"na_label\":\"NA\",\"opacity\":0.9,\"position\":\"bottomright\",\"type\":\"factor\",\"title\":\"Type d'intervention\",\"extra\":null,\"layerId\":null,\"className\":\"info legend\",\"group\":null}]}],\"limits\":{\"lat\":[11.39,50.63],\"lng\":[-4.4,7.1]},\"setView\":[[18,0],3,[]]},\"evals\":[],\"jsHooks\":[]}</script>\n```\n:::\n:::\n\n\n---\n\n## 🏅 Certifications & Distinctions\n\n::: {.award-card}\n**🏆 Prix des Pratiques Innovantes** — *Trophées de l'Eau et de l'Assainissement du Burkina Faso, 2024*  \nApplication de méthodes d'intelligence artificielle à la cartographie des ressources en eau.\n:::\n\n<div class=\"row g-3 mt-2\">\n  <div class=\"col-md-4\">\n    <div style=\"background:#112240;border:1px solid #1a3a6b;border-radius:0.5rem;padding:1rem;\">\n      <div style=\"color:#06d6a0;font-size:0.75rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:0.4rem;\">Certification</div>\n      <div style=\"font-weight:600;color:#cdd6f4;\">Brevet Européen des Premiers Secours (BEPS)</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:0.85rem;color:#7090a0;\">Croix-Rouge de Belgique — valable jusqu'en 2030</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"col-md-4\">\n    <div style=\"background:#112240;border:1px solid #1a3a6b;border-radius:0.5rem;padding:1rem;\">\n      <div style=\"color:#06d6a0;font-size:0.75rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:0.4rem;\">Formation</div>\n      <div style=\"font-weight:600;color:#cdd6f4;\">Osons l'Humanitaire — DIH</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:0.85rem;color:#7090a0;\">Croix-Rouge de Belgique — 2026</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"col-md-4\">\n    <div style=\"background:#112240;border:1px solid #1a3a6b;border-radius:0.5rem;padding:1rem;\">\n      <div style=\"color:#06d6a0;font-size:0.75rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:0.4rem;\">Formation continue</div>\n      <div style=\"font-weight:600;color:#cdd6f4;\">MOOC FUN, MOOC ADF, Udemy</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:0.85rem;color:#7090a0;\">R, Python, SIG, Machine Learning</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n---\n\n## 🌍 Langues\n\n| Langue   | Niveau     |\n|----------|------------|\n| Français | Courant    |\n| Anglais  | Débutant   |\n| Dioula   | Moyen      |\n| Grounssi | Moyen      |\n",
